body: I'd guess the `*.pb_text.cc` files are relying on an indirect inclusion that isn't present in @krantideep95's environment. One could add something that prints the appropriate `#include <algorithm>` line to [the code generator](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/51ef16057b4625e0a3e2943a9f1bbf856cf098ca/tensorflow/tools/proto_text/gen_proto_text_functions_lib.cc#L752).
